  "prompt": "Does Airtel provide franchises in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "Yes, Airtel does provide franchise opportunities in Hyderabad. Airtel, being one of the leading telecommunications service providers in India, offers various business opportunities including franchise models. These franchises typically involve setting up and managing Airtel retail stores that offer Airtel's products and services such as mobile, broadband, and DTH services.\n\nTo get detailed information about the franchise process, requirements, and application, you can visit the official Airtel website or contact their business support team directly. Here are the steps you might consider:\n\n1. **Visit the Airtel Website**: Look for a section on business opportunities or franchising.\n2. **Contact Airtel Business Support**: You can find contact details on their website to reach out to their franchise or business development team.\n3. **Inquiry and Application**: You'll likely need to fill out an application form and provide necessary documentation about your business capabilities and financial status.\n4. **Discussion and Agreement**: If your application is shortlisted, Airtel representatives will discuss the terms and you'll proceed with signing an agreement.\n\nIt's advisable to thoroughly research and understand the responsibilities and benefits of becoming an Airtel franchisee before making a decision.",
